general.name: photoUSNOBCamcol
general.description: Match of objects in a camcol of the SDSS imaging catalog to the USNO-B catalog . These matches are to any objects which are RUN_PRIMARY according to the local resolve (see resolve documentation ). See individual field files for full description.

changelog.description: Describes changes to the datamodel product and/or file structure from one release to another
